      <procstep>
        <procdesc>The paved surface layer was originally compiled from a 1995 flyover as two separate layers, major trans (polygon layer with edge of pavement, parking, bridges) and minor trans (arc layer with sidewalks and driveways). This data was updated and the two layers merged into one polygon layer from an April 17, 2003 flyover. Data was compiled using photogrammetric methods to meet ASPRS Class 1 accuracy standards for 1" = 100' scale mapping. All data sets were delivered in ARC/INFO coverage format. Data was converted to ESRI geodatabase format in 2004. Some significant road changes have been modified in-house and flagged in the attribute table.</procdesc>
